==Catalan==
===Etymology===
{{bor+|ca|mxi|*činče}}, itself from {{der|ca|la|cimex|cīmicem}} (cf. {{cog|es|chinche}}). The Catalan singular {{m|ca||xinxa}} is a back-formation from the plural {{m|ca|xinxes}}. Displaced {{cog|roa-oca|címeu}}, which was directly inherited from Latin.<ref>{{R:GDLC}}</ref>
